posts.post_content:
@Pinkmage   
Go back to Wow.   

This guy is nasty when he hits the board. 8 Mana is not that hard to get, even in 3 colors. You have to build your deck around doing these things, but still it is a different and fun way to play. There was some nasty Bolas Decks in Alara that was nothing but annoying LD and control until they got their win condition out, this planeswalker. And trust me, he is a win condition....
